LocHelpText="Your heavy weapon gains a bonus use."
LocFlyOverText="Rocketeer"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Heavy weapons are weapons such as the rocket launcher that can only be mounted on an EXO or WAR suit.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_Vanish X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Vanish"
LocLongDescription="If you begin your turn with no enemies able to see you, you gain concealment. This effect has a 2 turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="If you begin your turn with no enemies able to see you, you gain concealment."
LocFlyOverText="Vanish"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Units with Vanish make excellent scouts. If they get spotted, just retreat and regain concealment.<br/><Bullet/> There's no limit to the number of times a unit can regain concealment using Vanish.<br/><Bullet/> Vanish has a 2 turn cooldown. <br/>"

[ShadowOps_VanishTrigger X2AbilityTemplate]
